cleaningModal.title: Enhanced Clean
cleaningModal.description:
Kimiko committed to Airbnb’s 5-step enhanced cleaning process—a set of standards developed in partnership with experts, for the times of COVID-19 and beyond.

Here’s what Kimiko committed to doing before every stay:

items.title: Sanitize surfaces
items.subtitle: Sanitize every high-touch surface, down to the doorknob

items.title: Use approved products
items.subtitle: Use cleaners approved by health experts, like disinfectants with 70% alcohol or higher

items.title: Thoroughly clean
items.subtitle: Refer to our extensive checklists while cleaning room-by-room

items.title: Wear a mask and gloves
items.subtitle: Help avoid cross-contamination by wearing a mask and gloves

items.title: Wash all linens
items.subtitle: Wash linens at a high temperature setting

items.title: Follow all other local guidance
items.subtitle: Comply with local laws, including any additional safety or cleaning guidelines
